Bower:

    - bower is the automation tool , used to download the required dependencies to develop
      web application.

    - bower is the automation tool based on NodeJS Platform.

Install the bower:
------------------
>npm install -g bower


bower.json
----------
{
    "name":"durgasoft",
    "dependencies":{
        "bootstrap":"latest",
        "angular":"latest"
    }
}

>npm install


[Note : automatically dependencies will be downloads to "bower_components" folder]






